17. Reusable Components

Components can be reused across app.

const Button = ({ text }) => (
  <button className="px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded">{text}</button>
);

Interview Qs

Q: Why are components reusable in React?
A: Because they are modular, independent, and accept props.

18. Structured Code

React projects follow folder structure (components, pages, hooks, utils).

Helps maintainability and teamwork.

Interview Qs

Q: Why structure matters?
A: Easier scaling, debugging, collaboration.
